<bibRefCitation author="Anufriev, GA" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de l'academie polonaise des sciences, serie des sciences biologiques" pageId="18" pageNumber="321" pagination="721 - 726" refId="B1" refString="Anufriev, GA, 1971. Study of leafhoppers from the tribe Signoretiini (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha) with descriptions of two new species of Signoretia Stal from western Africa. Bulletin de l'academie polonaise des sciences, serie des sciences biologiques 19: 721 - 726" title="Study of leafhoppers from the tribe Signoretiini (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha) with descriptions of two new species of Signoretia Stal from western Africa." volume="19" year="1971">
