<bibRefCitation author="Linnavuori, R" journalOrPublisher="Entomotaxonomia" pageId="18" pageNumber="321" refId="B12" refString="Linnavuori, R, 1978. Revision of the African Cicadellidae (subfamilies Nioniinae, Signoretiinae and Drabescinae) (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Annales Entomologici Fennici 44: 33-48." title="Revision of the African Cicadellidae (subfamilies Nioniinae, Signoretiinae and Drabescinae) (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Annales Entomologici Fennici 44: 33 - 48." year="1978">
